### kubectl commands
`kubectl get all`

`kubectl get nodes`

`kubectl get pod`

`kubectl get services`

`kubectl get deployment`

`kubectl get replicaset`

### debugging
`kubectl logs {pod-name}`

`kubectl describe [{pod-name}, {deployment-name}, {service-name},..}`

`kubectl exec -it {pod-name} -- bin/bash`

### delete pod
`kubectl delete pod/{pod-name}`
